name: La señora Muerte
description: Does the afterlife world colour blue or violet? Or is it pure darkness? As a child, I always being told the importance of chrysanthemum flowers. It is the flower of death and in Japanese tattoo society, we believed that having Yellow chrysanthemum tattoo with us, is also an indication that we embrace our destiny. How would we know if it is our time, are the angles of death actually watching our light fading or they are waiting for the smoke to go out. All I could imagine is someone behind our dimension are always watching and waiting. This NFT is a representation of what's behind my mind at night. Are we really alone? Maybe not.
